Package: flights
Version: 0.1
Title: Data about On-Time Performance of flights in the US
Author: A Srinivasan
Maintainer: A Srinivasan <arunkumar.sriniv@gmail.com>
Depends: R (>= 2.15.0)
Imports: tools, methods, data.table (>= 1.9.5)
Description: The package contains flights, flight delays and weather information of all flights that departed from NYC in 2014 (currently Jan-Oct). It also contains functions to facilitate automated download of On-Time Performance flight stats from the Beareau of Transportation Statistics for any given year. To do: add automation for obtaining weather report as well.
License: CC0
URL: https://github.com/arunsrinivasan/flights
BugReports: https://github.com/arunsrinivasan/flights/issues
